summary: This is an FBI internal notification from the Newark/Trenton Resident Agency to the Miami/Palm Beach Resident Agency, stating that a lead regarding an obstruction of justice investigation (Case ID 72-MM-113327) has been covered following an interview conducted on October 12, 2010. The document references an enclosed FD-302 form detailing the interview.

persons.name: Alfredo Rodriguez
persons.context: Appears as the drafting or approving agent for the lead notification from the Newark/Trenton Resident Agency.

events.title: Interview regarding obstruction of justice
events.description: An interview was conducted as part of the investigation into case 72-MM-113327 (Obstruction of Justice). The details were documented in an FD-302 form.

keyFacts: The document is an FBI lead notification related to an obstruction of justice investigation (Case ID 72-MM-113327).
An interview was conducted on October 12, 2010, and its details are contained in an enclosed FD-302 form.
The Newark/Trenton Resident Agency notified the Miami/Palm Beach Resident Agency that the lead was considered covered.
The document's primary purpose is administrative, confirming the completion of an investigative step.
